            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c832004a59a1477f-f09fcd twpub-c832004a59a1477f-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section  2.  Information about the Mission of Project Gutenberg-tm</h4></div>"
