        "$:/plugins/twpub/c832004a59a1477f/text/000001737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c832004a59a1477f/text/000001737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c832004a59a1477f-f09fcd twpub-c832004a59a1477f-6b4cd0\"><p>Project Gutenberg-tm is synonymous with the free distribution of\nelectronic works in formats readable by the widest variety of computers\nincluding obsolete, old, middle-aged and new computers.  It exists\nbecause of the efforts of hundreds of volunteers and donations from\npeople in all walks of life.</p></div>"
